snippet.textDisplay: I had vitamin D deficiency for years and didn't take my supplement. Covid hit and I ended hospitalized and the drs found that i had the vitamin D deficit as well and prediabetic. this video explain why I almost died. Thank you so much for explaining this in such a details. I'm making changes to my life to make sure my vitamin D levels are healthy again. Happy to be alive!
